{
  "page": "Cave near Greyguard",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg/350px-Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"364\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg/525px-Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dd/Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg/700px-Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> in the grotto, by Marc Simonetti ©</div></div></div>\n<p>A <b>cave near Greyguard</b> is found <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapters_that_take_place_at_the_cave\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapters that take place at the cave</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cave_near_Greyguard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The cave is found beneath a hill in the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> between <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedoor\" title=\"Stonedoor\">Stonedoor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Greyguard\" title=\"Greyguard\">Greyguard</a>, two abandoned castles of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> along the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Facing north, the narrow mouth of the cave is concealed behind a <a href=\"/index.php/Soldier_pine\" title=\"Soldier pine\">soldier pine</a>. A passage then descends twenty feet into a large cavern the size of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Great Hall of Winterfell\">Great Hall of Winterfell</a>. The cavern has a shallow pool, and a sinkhole in the center of the chamber leads to a possibly-larger cavern below. An underground stream can be heard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Numerous columns and stalactites can be found in a dim back room with walls of rose and white flowstone. A dark hole under an outthrust of wet stone leads to a grotto, in which a little waterfall fills a wide pool of pale green water. Another passage from the grotto leads deeper into the cave system.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cave_near_Greyguard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cave_near_Greyguard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, feigning desertion from the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>, accompanies <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> raiders led by <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Magnar_of_Thenn\" title=\"Magnar of Thenn\">Magnar of Thenn</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a> as they head through the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a> toward the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>. The company stays overnight in the cavern, with their horses hobbled by the shallow pool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Climbing the hill, Jon tells <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a> to head to <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>, as the <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a> would not be able to climb the Wall with them. One of the <a href=\"/index.php/Thenns\" title=\"Thenns\">Thenns</a> brings Jon into the cave, where he is questioned by Styr and Jarl about patrols of the Watch along the Wall.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a>, Jon's lover, hears water and explores the grotto and nearby passage. When Jon finds her in the grotto, Ygritte tells him that all of the caves in the hilly region connect, and she tells the story of <a href=\"/index.php/Gendel\" title=\"Gendel\">Gendel</a> becoming lost in <a href=\"/index.php/Gorne%27s_Way\" title=\"Gorne&#39;s Way\">Gorne's Way</a>. The pair have sex in the grotto before returning to the other wildlings in the cavern.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The raiding party climbs the Wall the next day,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and they descend at <a href=\"/index.php/Greyguard\" title=\"Greyguard\">Greyguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Jon escapes the wildlings at <a href=\"/index.php/Queenscrown\" title=\"Queenscrown\">Queenscrown</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and Ygritte is killed in Styr's <a href=\"/index.php/Attack_on_Castle_Black\" title=\"Attack on Castle Black\">attack on Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cave_near_Greyguard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Within the rock, the passage descended twenty feet before it opened out onto a space as large as <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Great Hall of Winterfell\">Great Hall</a>. Cookfires burned amongst the columns, their smoke rising to blacken the stony ceiling. The horses had been hobbled along one wall, beside a shallow pool. A sinkhole in the center of the floor opened on what might have been an even greater cavern below, though the darkness made it hard to tell. Jon could hear the soft rushing sound of an underground stream somewhere below as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Let's not go back t' <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a>. Let's go down inside, and join up with <a href=\"/index.php/Gendel\" title=\"Gendel\">Gendel</a>'s children. I don't ever want t' leave this cave, Jon Snow. Not ever.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Ygritte</b>: D'you remember that cave? We should have stayed in that cave. I told you so.<br />\n</p><p><b>Jon</b>: We'll go back to the cave. You're not going to die, Ygritte. You're not.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Ygritte</b>: Oh. You know nothing, Jon Snow.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapters_that_take_place_at_the_cave\">Chapters that take place at the cave</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cave_near_Greyguard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Chapters that take place at the cave\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 26\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i>: 26. Jon III</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cave_near_Greyguard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos26.7B.7B.7B